quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  23,18,"Min njippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagoore nde], Min ndewni …óam ka leydi, pellet, Minen ko Nden Hattan…ďe e dow na…ďugol …óam."
  23,19,"Min pu…ó…óani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on ndeer ton dim…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko e majje √Īaamoton."
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hangal fu…óina gu∆īam [nebban wujetee…óam] e li'am [maafir…óam] wonan'de √Īaamoo…ďe."
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraa…ói …ói tasakuyee, Mi…óen njarna on bo…ó…óum e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafooje keew…óe, ko immorde e majji kadi √Īaamoton."
  23,22,"Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laa…óe …óe ndoonndete…óon."
  23,23,"GooŇč…óii Min Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ďe makko …ďe o maaki : eey mon yo yim…ďe am, ndewee Alla. Dewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori mo. Enee, on kulatah?"."
  23,24,"Hooree…ďe mbatu ngun mbii'ani …ďen yeddu…ďe immorde e yim…ďe makko …ďen: "Oo wonaani si ko o …ďanndiŇčke yeru mo'on homo faalaa nde o …ďurnotoo e dow moo…óon. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaaji, min naniraani …óum baabiraa…ďe amen aran…ďe …ďen"."
  23,25,"KaŇčko o wonaani si wonaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'um, habbitee mo tun haa see…óa."
  23,26,"O maaki: "Joom am, wallam e ko …ďe njennimi kon"."
  23,27,"Min wahayini fa'ade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore amen nden arii hu…ď…ďinirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naatu e ndeer makka immorde e kala nooneeji …óin …ói…ói-…ói…ói. E koreeji ma, si wonaa …ďeen konngol ngol aditii e mu'um, wata a haaldu e am fii …ďen too√Īu…ďe, pellet, kam…ďe ko …ďe yooletee…ďe."